CBRE is thrilled to present 18-71 Harcourt Road, Altona for lease.

Located in the heart of Altona, one of Melbourne’s most tightly held industrial precincts. This property offers occupiers ease of access to major arterials including the Princes Freeway via Kororoit Creek Road providing a direct link to the West Gate Freeway and Western Rig Road.

Located approximately 12km* west of the Port of Melbourne, 16km* west of the CBD and 21km south of Melbourne Airport.

18-71 Harcourt Road boasts the following key features:
+ Brand new speculatively developed facility
+ Total Site Area: 20,289sqm*
+ Total Building Area: 9,146sqm*
+ High clearance warehouse: 8,658sqm*
+ Dual level corporate office and staff amenities: 488sqm*
+ Four (4) on-grade roller shutter doors
+ Four (4) recessed loading docks
+ ESFR sprinkler system
+ Separate car and truck entry/exit
+ Security fencing
+ Ample on-site car parking

Please contact the listed CBRE agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.

*approx.

CBRE is excited to offer for lease this outstanding industrial facility. The property boasts loads of unique features that are difficult to find, in addition the facility is only minutes away from multiple freeway access points. 

The key features include:
•	4 container height roller doors
•	High clearance workshop style facility 
•	7,500sqm* of genuine crushed rock hardstand 
•	Secure perimeter fencing
•	Wash bay & triple interceptor 
•	Total building area: 1,750sqm*
•	Corporate office &staff amenities (including elevator) 
•	Site area:  11,275sqm*
•	1km* to Millers Junction retail precinct 

This one won’t last long. Contact the exclusive agency team below to find out more, or to arrange an inspection. 

*approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer 23 Burns Road, Altona, for lease.

The office space at 23 Burns Road Altona is perfectly located for access to Melbourne’s freeway network. 

Fully fitted office, ready to occupy, with full glass elevations affording excellent natural light to both levels. 

Key property features:
+ Phone data and power points throughout
+ Glass partitioning
+ Furnished if required
+ Ducted heating and cooling
+ Suspended acoustic tiled ceilings
+ Security system 
+ Natural light from three directions
+ Kitchenettes over two levels 
+ Air-conditioned comms room
+ Board/meeting rooms on both levels 
+ One traffic light to freeway network
+ 11 car parks plus additional space

For further information, please contact the team from CBRE.

*approx.
